import React from 'react'; import { Segment, Grid, Icon, Table, Tab } from 'semantic-ui-react'; import {format} from 'date-fns'; import { IAffilie } from '../../../app/models/affilie'; const AffilieDetailedInfo: React.FC<{affilie: IAffilie}> = ({affilie}) => { const panes = [ { menuItem: 'Dossiers Payés', render: () => N Dossier Date Paiement Fr Engage AMO MPSC TOTAL T.Dossier {affilie.Qps.map(qp => qp.observation != 'Med' ? ( {qp.nDossier} {format(qp.datePaiementReel, 'EEEE d MMMM yyyy') } {qp.fraisEngage} {qp.rembAmo} {qp.rembMpsc} {qp.totalRemb} {qp.observation} ):( {qp.nDossier} {format(qp.datePaiementReel, 'EEEE d MMMM yyyy') } {qp.fraisEngage} {qp.rembAmo} {qp.rembMpsc} {qp.totalRemb} {qp.observation} ) )}
}, { menuItem: 'Retenues', render: () => Id Pai Date Montant 303 304 Date.S T.Payement {affilie.QpMois.map(qpm => {qpm.idPai} {format(qpm.date, 'EEEE d MMMM yyyy') } {qpm.qp} {qpm.code303} {qpm.code304} {format(qpm.dateSaisie, 'EEEE d MMMM yyyy') } {qpm.typePai} )}
}, { menuItem: 'Tab 3', render: () => Tab 3 Content }, ] return ( ); }; export default AffilieDetailedInfo;
